desc:
Once per turn: You can target 1 Ritual Monster you control; reveal 1 Ritual Monster in your hand (until the end of this turn), and if you do, its Level becomes the same as the targeted monster's, until the end of this turn. Once per turn, if "Ruin, Queen of Oblivion" or "Demise, King of Armageddon" is Ritual Summoned to your field: You can activate 1 of these effects;
● Draw 1 card.
● Destroy 1 card on the field.
